<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
	<title>Privacy Policy — Nudge</title>
	<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/nudge-icon.png" />
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:opsz,wght@9..40,400;9..40,500;9..40,600&family=Instrument+Serif&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>

	<header class="nav">
		<div class="container nav-inner">
			<a href="/" class="nav-brand">
				<img src="/nudge-icon.png" alt="" width="32" height="32" />
				<span>Nudge</span>
			</a>
			<a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to home</a>
		</div>
	</header>

	<main class="container">
		<article class="legal">
			<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="updated">Last updated: March 20, 2026</p>

			<p>Aleph ("we", "our", "us") operates the Nudge application ("App") for Clover POS devices. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

			<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
			<p>When you use the App, we may access the following data through the Clover platform:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Order Data:</strong> Current order line items (product names, quantities, prices) to generate real-time suggestions</li>
				<li><strong>Inventory Data:</strong> Your product catalog and inventory levels to ensure suggestions reference available items</li>
				<li><strong>Usage Statistics:</strong> Aggregated metrics such as suggestions shown, accepted, and dismissed, stored locally on the device</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>To generate AI-powered upsell and cross-sell suggestions during active orders</li>
				<li>To display performance statistics within the App</li>
				<li>To improve the quality and relevance of suggestions</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>3. Data Processing</h2>
			<p>Order context is sent to our AI service provider to generate suggestions. This data is processed in real time and is not stored by the AI provider beyond the duration of the request. No personally identifiable customer information is transmitted.</p>

			<h2>4. Data Storage</h2>
			<p>Usage statistics (suggestion counts, acceptance rates) are stored locally on your Clover device using SharedPreferences. We do not maintain a separate cloud database of your merchant data.</p>

			<h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
			<p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your data to third parties. Data may be shared only:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>With our AI service provider, solely to generate suggestions (no data retention)</li>
				<li>When required by law or legal process</li>
				<li>To protect our rights or the safety of users</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>6. Data Security</h2>
			<p>We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data, including HTTPS encryption for all API communications and leveraging the Clover platform's built-in security model.</p>

			<h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
			<p>You may:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Uninstall the App at any time to stop all data access</li>
				<li>Clear local statistics through the App's settings</li>
				<li>Contact us to request information about your data</li>
			</ul>

			<h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
			<p>The App is designed for business use and is not directed at individuals under the age of 18.</p>

			<h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
			<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected by the "Last updated" date above. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

			<h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
			<p>For questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at <strong>privacy@alephlabs.com</strong>.</p>
		</article>
	</main>

	<footer class="footer">
		<div class="container footer-inner">
			<span>&copy; 2026 Nudge. All rights reserved.</span>
			<nav>
				<a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
				<a href="/eula">Terms</a>
			</nav>
		</div>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
	:root {
		--brand: #1B6B4A;
		--brand-dark: #0F4D35;
		--brand-surface: #E8F5EE;
		--surface-1: #FAFBF9;
		--text-1: #1A2B23;
		--text-2: #5A6B63;
		--text-3: #8A9B93;
		--text-on-brand: #F5FBF8;
		--border: #E2E8E4;
	}

	*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
	html { -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }

	body {
		font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
		font-size: 16px;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--text-1);
		background: var(--surface-1);
	}

	img { display: block; }
	a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

	.container { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

	.nav {
		padding: 14px 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
		margin-bottom: 48px;
	}
	.nav-inner {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 24px;
	}
	.nav-brand {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 10px;
		font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
		font-size: 22px;
	}
	.nav-brand img { border-radius: 8px; width: 32px; height: 32px; }
	.back-link {
		font-size: 14px;
		font-weight: 500;
		color: var(--text-2);
		transition: color 200ms ease;
	}
	.back-link:hover { color: var(--brand); }

	.legal { padding-bottom: 64px; }
	.legal h1 {
		font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
		font-size: 36px;
		line-height: 1.15;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		margin-bottom: 8px;
	}
	.updated {
		color: var(--text-3);
		font-size: 14px;
		margin-bottom: 32px;
	}
	.legal h2 {
		font-size: 18px;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--text-1);
		margin-top: 32px;
		margin-bottom: 12px;
	}
	.legal p {
		color: var(--text-2);
		margin-bottom: 16px;
	}
	.legal ul {
		color: var(--text-2);
		margin-bottom: 16px;
		padding-left: 24px;
	}
	.legal li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
	.legal strong { color: var(--text-1); font-weight: 600; }
	.legal a { color: var(--brand); text-decoration: underline; }

	.footer {
		padding: 24px 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}
	.footer-inner {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 24px;
		font-size: 13px;
		color: var(--text-3);
	}
	.footer-inner nav { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
	.footer-inner a { transition: color 200ms ease; }
	.footer-inner a:hover { color: var(--text-1); }
</style>
